reviews.review_text: clarity  I love the clarity of the instruments here. i can really hear everyone.weir"s guitar is present and really cool, piano is perfect, the one drum kit is not to busy, but very supportive and the bass is wicked loud, the bass solos in eyes are great.Phil is really going for it all through the show, I love to hear that! I had some of this on a fuzzy old second hand tape for years, it really instilled my grateful dead mania! thanks to the archive again; what a service.
